Customer Success Group

Salesforce Success Plans gives every customer access to resources, guidance, and support at every step of the journey.

Highlights for Summer ’24 include:
Success Plans for Tableau
Standard, Premier, and Signature Success Plans are now available for Tableau.
Enhanced Signature Success Plan Experience
Signature customers can now collaborate with their designated Customer Success Manager.
Customer Success Score Enhancements
Improved personalized benchmarking: Score is now based on an individual account.
Signature Success Plan for Marketing Cloud Intelligence
Signature provides a personalized proactive partnership managed by a designated Customer Success Manager.

Heroku

Heroku is a cloud-based application platform for building and deploying web apps.

For information on new features, go to the Heroku Changelog.

IdeaExchange

Share ideas with the Trailblazer community and Salesforce product managers.

Trailhead GO

The newest release includes new widgets as well as enhancements to the Trailblazer Profile and Trailblazer Community.
Easily access learning right from your mobile home screen by adding a Trailhead widget on iOS, MacOS, and Android devices.
Now, you can “upvote” answers you find most helpful in the Trailblazer Community.
